<p>This page contains information about the effort to build UE4 natively on a Linux host.  If you are looking for information about targeting Linux using the existing Mac or Windows tools please see <a href="/Compiling_For_Linux" title="Compiling For Linux">Compiling For Linux</a>. The main page is <a href="/Linux_Support" title="Linux Support">Linux support</a>.
</p>
